To engage with Tortoise, users need a Farcaster account, which can be created via farcaster.xyz or the Warpcast client (available on iOS and Android). Once signed in, users can visit https://farcaster.xyz/~/channel/tortoise directly or search for “Tortoise” in Warpcast’s channel discovery page (warpcast.com/~/mini-apps). Following the channel integrates its casts into your home feed, ensuring you stay updated on discussions without leaving the Farcaster interface.
